<br>
With tha targetting change... it be a dangerous thing to be vulnerable to invisible foes. Ifn ya cannae see invis, ya cannae target.<br>
<br>
Qeynos Badge of Honor and problem solved for yerself, tho a Bracer of tha Hidden tho rare helps yer whole group.<br>
<br>
Oh and little known fact it seems. Castin Invis to Undead on yerself will cause a loss o target in tha same fashion. Can be useful against a rogue withoot see invis in yer case Valya. Give ya time ter rest up ifn ya move away yerself and cast Itu.<br>
